<p>I&#8217;ve read <a href="http://gembundler.com/rationale.html">Bundler&#8217;s documentation</a> recently because I wanted to better understand how it is supposed to be used. My learning has been a bit difficult for a simple reason: there is a lot of text on Bundler&#8217;s website, but no real concrete scenario explained with a good old image. So I&#8217;ve decided to share the one I&#8217;ve built during my learning:</p>
